        "title": "java cast error:[Ljava.lang.Byte; incompatible with [B",
        "body": "<p>I have encounterd a starnge java cast error.<\/p>\n\n<p>when I cast some object to byte[],<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>byte [] a = new byte[lenght];\na = (byte[])obj;//obj is actually a byte array with the same number of elements\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>I encounter the following error<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>[Ljava.lang.Byte; incompatible with [B\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>What causes this ?\nThanks in advance for your insight.<\/p>\n",
